        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mdl-grid home__getstarted">
      <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col">
        <h2>Let's Get Started</h2>
        <p>
          <a class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--accent home__getstarted__button" href="<%= Settings.client_url %>/users/sign_up">
            Activate your regular check
          </a>
          <a class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised home__getstarted__button" href="<%= Settings.client_url %>/users/sign_in">
            Sign in
